acceptCreditLineLender(bytes32).details: used to Accept a credit line by a specified lender

params._creditLineHash: Credit line hash which represents the credit Line Unique Hash

calculateCurrentDebt(bytes32).details: Used to calculate current debt of borrower against a credit line.

params._creditLineHash: Hash of the credit line for which current debt has to be calculated

calculateInterestAccrued(bytes32).details: Used to calculate interest accrued since last repayment

params.creditLineHash: Hash of the credit line for which interest accrued has to be calculated

returns._0: uint256 interest accrued over current borrowed amount since last repayment

calculateInterestPerSecond(uint256,uint2.details: Used to Calculate Interest Per second on given principal and Interest rate

params._borrowRate: It is the Interest Rate at which Credit Line is approved
params._principal: principal Amount for which interest has to be calculated.

returns._0: uint256 interest per second for the given parameters

closeCreditLine(bytes32).details: used to close credit line once by borrower or lender

params.creditLineHash: Credit line hash which represents the credit Line Unique Hash

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

repay(bytes32,bool,uint256).details: used to repay assest to credit line

params._creditLineHash: Credit line hash which represents the credit Line Unique Hash
params._repayAmount: amount which borrower wants to repay to credit line

requestCreditLineToLender(address,uint25.details: used to request a credit line by a borrower

params._borrowLimit: maximum borrow amount in a credit line
params._borrowRate: Interest Rate at which credit Line is requested
params._lender: lender from whom creditLine is requested

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
